# 🔥 Tricky Interview Questions

---

## 1. Output?

```javascript
async function test() {
    console.log("A");
    await Promise.resolve();
    console.log("B");
}

console.log("C");
test();
console.log("D");
```

### Output:

```
C
A
D
B
```

👉 हिंदी:

* await async को queue में डाल देता है

---

## 2. await vs setTimeout

```javascript
async function test() {
    await Promise.resolve();
    console.log("Promise");
}

setTimeout(() => console.log("Timeout"), 0);

test();
```

### Output:

```
Promise
Timeout
```

👉 Promise > setTimeout

