# 🔥 forEach vs for...of (Important)

---

## ❌ Wrong

```javascript
arr.forEach(async (item) => {
    await doSomething(item);
});
```

👉 Doesn’t wait properly

---

## ✅ Correct

```javascript
for (let item of arr) {
    await doSomething(item);
}
```

---

