# 🔥 Q7: Loop Trap 😈

```javascript
let arr = [1, 2, 3];

arr.forEach(async (num) => {
    await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1000));
    console.log(num);
});
```

### ❓ Output?

```
1
2
3   (almost same time)
```

👉 NOT sequential

---

### ✅ Correct:

```javascript
for (let num of arr) {
    await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1000));
    console.log(num);
}
```

👉 हिंदी: forEach await को respect नहीं करता

